metadata.description: The I'm a Kitty Cat NFT project consists of 10,000 Kitty Cat generative art NFTs from metaverse pioneer Carrie Tatsu, legendary award-winning artist Massimo Righi, and CG art guru Fred Becerra. All are photo-real cats with gorgeous visible traits. The drop also boasts a community of cat lovers and we are giving away funds to our holders' chosen charities. We are also developing an Augmented Reality app that will bring these NFTs to life and allow you to earn tokens and level up your kitty! #purrfect!
metadata.name: I'm A Kitty Cat #1
